{"tid":1605880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【10.1馬照跑】馬會宣佈賽事如期舉行 不會有警察於場內當值站崗","createTime":"2019-09-30T12:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:27:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e0f197f02f278235dba6f4ba55f859050ddda6","tid":1605880,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"馬會今晚（30日）宣佈國慶賽馬日，將於明天（10月1日）如期在沙田馬場舉行，並會繼續密切留意最新的情況。<br />\n<br />\n會方表示因應目前的環境，明天賽馬日將會加強進場保安檢查，並呼籲馬迷預留充裕時間接受安檢，並希望馬迷可以切勿攜帶可能對人馬安全構成危險的物品。<br />\n<br />\n馬會強調在舉辦賽事時，一向以安全為首要考慮，盡責任確保賽駒、馬迷、騎師及員工時刻安全，並感謝馬迷的體諒及耐性。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，沙田馬場將在明天中午12時播放中國國歌，屆時將不會像往年同日般，由警察銀樂隊進行吹奏及合唱，而開場後所舉行的兩項分級賽（第三場國慶盃及第七場慶典盃），在賽後頒獎時亦不會一如既往地播放中國國歌。<br />\n<br />\n此外，明天沙田馬場也不會像平日跑馬那樣，有警察於場內當值站崗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/20190930/KTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20190930%2FKTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=448b1a6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20190930%2FKTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE%2F&h=6ce46688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/20190930/KTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE/</a>"},{"pid":"7ec1106637641811d87c72b35bf5d3b1a7bea5c2","tid":1605880,"uid":901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"全民TG 改狗竇住址為名<br />\n<br />\n日日夜夜提醒D狗仔狗女住邊<br />\n<br />\n咁鍾意mon group吖嗱？"},{"pid":"977e76e9e5f188a6c518545be8c1465c1f396526","tid":1605880,"uid":275730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e0f197f02f278235dba6f4ba55f859050ddda6","tid":1605880,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"馬會今晚（30日）宣佈國慶賽馬日，將於明天（10月1日）如期在沙田馬場舉行，並會繼續密切留意最新的情況。<br />\n<br />\n會方表示因應目前的環境，明天賽馬日將會加強進場保安檢查，並呼籲馬迷預留充裕時間接受安檢，並希望馬迷可以切勿攜帶可能對人馬安全構成危險的物品。<br />\n<br />\n馬會強調在舉辦賽事時，一向以安全為首要考慮，盡責任確保賽駒、馬迷、騎師及員工時刻安全，並感謝馬迷的體諒及耐性。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，沙田馬場將在明天中午12時播放中國國歌，屆時將不會像往年同日般，由警察銀樂隊進行吹奏及合唱，而開場後所舉行的兩項分級賽（第三場國慶盃及第七場慶典盃），在賽後頒獎時亦不會一如既往地播放中國國歌。<br />\n<br />\n此外，明天沙田馬場也不會像平日跑馬那樣，有警察於場內當值站崗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/20190930/KTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20190930%2FKTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE%2F&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=448b1a6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2F20190930%2FKTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE%2F&h=6ce46688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/20190930/KTDYMUSWAYALVRBZHRGXOPCGSE/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:15:34.000Z","msg":"又唔係有何妖隻馬"},{"pid":"492a0caa486077649c66735b1097bd1a9055c47f","tid":1605880,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"不會有警察於場內當值站崗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又想玩721</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">定係有狗扮恐怖份子</span>"},{"pid":"d8bf564dcf5111505ed5d81c2745e5ca9ccee7f1","tid":1605880,"uid":279095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"馬會認同警察係暴力源頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99324d6ce988e0a6fccf3eb63ca0b378d176b2d2","tid":1605880,"uid":265133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:27:47.000Z","msg":"無警察等於安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}